            <lg xml:id="TK41">
<l>ilvāḻvā ṉeṉpā ṉiyalpuṭaiya mūvarkku</l>
<l>nallāṟṟi ṉiṉṟa tuṇai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He is a householder who is a companion on the good path</l>
<l>trod by the three good ones.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
